Subject:        Directions to the Tamiment Resort and Conference Center,  location of the 20th Annual Conference


Dear Participants:

Here are the Directions to the Tamiment:

From New York & Points East: West on I-80 to Delaware Water Gap to bridge crossing into PA. Continue to Exit 52 --- Marshalls Creek, get off the exit and take 209 North to Bushkill. Turn left at the blinker traffic light (onto Bushkill Falls Road) and Tamiment is 4 miles up the hill.

From Philadelphia and Points South: North on the NE Extension (I-476) of the PA Turnpike to Exit 33 (Lehigh Valley). Proceed East on Route 22 to Route 33 North, which then meets I-80 East. Take 80 East to Exit 52. Get off and take 209 North Bushkill .Turn left at the blinker Traffic light and Tamiment is 4 miles up the hill.

From Washington and Baltimore: Take I-83 North to junction of I-81. Proceed North on I-81 to junction of I-78 to Route 33 North. Then Proceed as indicated on directions fron Philadelphia.

From Connecticut and New England: West on I-84 to 209 South. South on 209 to Bushkill. Turn right at blinker traffic light (onto Bushkill Falls Road) and Tamiment is 4 miles up the hill.

If you have any questions or concerns please feel free to contact me.

Sincerely,

